	<TextEquiv>
	<Unicode>Behind the deterioration is a conver-
gence of factors, say analysts both inside
and outside the Defense Department. New
military systems are more technologi-
cally complex than ever before, and they
rely increasingly on unproven technolo-
gies. Defense programs are now “so mas-</Unicode></TextEquiv>
